Package: FacPad
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Sparse Factor Analysis model for the inference of
        pathways responsive to drug treatment
Version: 3.0
Date: 2014-03-25
Author: Haisu Ma
Maintainer: Haisu Ma <haisu.ma.pku.2008@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.12.1),Rlab,MASS
Description: This method tries to explain the gene-wise treatment response ratios in terms of the latent pathways. It uses bayesian sparse factor modeling to infer the loadings (weights) of each pathway on its associated probesets as well as the latent factor activity levels for each treatment.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
Packaged: 2014-03-27 22:56:46 UTC; Evelyn
NeedsCompilation: no
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2014-03-28 00:31:36
